title: Carb Smart Chicken Breasts with Balsamic Onions and Parmesan Veggies
description: This dish will have you licking your lips in anticipation! Tender onions melt in a rich balsamic sauce, all spooned over juicy chicken breast. On the side, savoury Parmesan veggies are a perfect balance for the balsamic onions' natural sweetness!

